(4, 'Sands Deluxe Room', '1', 'Deluxe', '<p>The Sands Deluxe Room offers a luxurious and comfortable stay for those seeking a premium experience. Featuring elegant decor, modern amenities, and spacious layouts, this room is designed to provide a relaxing retreat for guests.</p><p><br></p><p>Key features of the Sands Deluxe Room may include:</p><p><br></p><p>1. Stylish Interiors: The room is tastefully decorated with high-quality furnishings, soothing color schemes, and attention to detail, creating an inviting ambiance for guests.</p><p><br></p><p>2. Comfortable Accommodations: Guests can enjoy a plush king-sized bed or twin beds with premium linens, ensuring a restful night\'s sleep. Ample seating areas and workspaces are also provided for convenience.</p><p><br></p><p>3. Modern Amenities: The room is equipped with modern conveniences such as a flat-screen TV, minibar, coffee/tea maker, and high-speed internet access, catering to both leisure and business travelers.</p><p><br></p><p>4. Luxurious Bathroom: The en-suite bathroom features a spacious shower, bathtub, and deluxe toiletries, offering a spa-like experience for guests to unwind and rejuvenate.</p><p><br></p><p>5. Scenic Views: Depending on the location, Sands Deluxe Rooms may offer stunning views of the city skyline, lush gardens, or serene waterfront, enhancing the overall stay experience.</p><p><br></p><p>6. Personalized Services: Guests staying in Sands Deluxe Rooms often enjoy personalized services such as 24-hour room service, concierge assistance, and access to exclusive facilities like fitness centers or swimming pools.</p><p><br></p><p>Whether for a leisurely getaway or a business trip, the Sands Deluxe Room provides a blend of luxury, comfort, and convenience, ensuring a memorable stay for discerning travelers.</p>', 3, 5, 2, 2, 500, 1, 'main_1713609586.jpg', 1, '2024-04-20 10:28:00', '2024-04-20 10:39:46'),
